Package: wattline-rtl8761b
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: aarch64_cortex-a53
Maintainer: Keith Ahner
Depends: wattline-bt
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Verified RTL8761B Bluetooth driver for GL-X3000 Linux 5.4.211
 Installs a pinned GL.iNet ABI-compatible btusb/btrtl/btintel module set and
 Realtek firmware for supported RTL8761B USB adapters. Refuses other kernels.
